&lt;p&gt;We are delighted to be able to advertise for a new and exciting post of Specialist Simulation Clinical Lecturer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thie post holder will strategically lead on the implementation, maintenance and growth of the simulation department within the Trust and harnessing their use within medical and clinical education.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop an awareness of growth areas in simulation and clinical skills technology in order to improve and enhance facilities by engaging with key personnel with simulation technology and research.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Appraise and evaluate service delivery and role development in order to promote further simulation training provision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To take the lead role in the trusts partnership with external organisations, such as Health Education North East and Cumbria, Health Education Hull and Yorkshire&lt;/p&gt;
